    <section id="HC8477E8AA7434D28A60DF409764F80EE">
      <enum>2.</enum>
      <header>Climate
			 variability review</header>
      <text display-inline="no-display-inline">
        <cato:entity xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="law-citation">
          <cato:entity-ref entity-type="act" value="Reclamation States Emergency Drought Relief Act of 1991/s:203/ss:e">Subsection
			 (e) of section 203 of the Reclamation States Emergency Drought Relief Act of
			 1991</cato:entity-ref> (<cato:entity-ref entity-type="uscode" value="usc/43/2223/e">43 U.S.C. 2223(e)</cato:entity-ref>)</cato:entity> is amended as follows:</text>
			<quoted-block id="H0430BE03DEAF44F2925EDA5793508AAE" style="OLC">
				<subsection id="H9EE37FC479B347879DF52DA194FF85E4">
          <enum>(e)</enum>
          <header>Review</header>
          <text>The
				contingency plans shall include provisions for periodic review to assure
				adequacy of the contingency plan to respond to current conditions, as well as
				address projected long-term climate variability and change, and such plans may
				be modified
				accordingly.</text>
				</subsection>
        <after-quoted-block>.</after-quoted-block>
      </quoted-block>
